## agGridMaterialFontFace variable

The AG Material font face used on ag-theme-material Grid Pro theme.

**Signature:**

```typescript
agGridMaterialFontFace = "\n  @font-face {\n    font-family: \"agGridMaterial\";\n    src: url(data:font/woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,);\n    font-weight: normal;\n    font-style: normal;\n  }\n"
```
